	const line_map_ordinary *, removing call to
	linemap_check_ordinary.
	(LINEMAP_LINE): Likewise.
	(LINEMAP_SYSP): Likewise.
	(linemap_resolve_location): Strengthen final param from
	const line_map ** to const line_map_ordinary **.
