	(add_dir): Likewise.
	* mkdeps.c (munge): Use XNEWVEC.
	(deps_init): Use XCNEW.
	(deps_add_target): Use XRESIZEVEC.
	(deps_add_default_target): Cast return value of alloca.
	(deps_add_dep): Use XRESIZEVEC.
	(deps_add_vpath): Likewise.  Use XNEWVEC too.
	(deps_restore): Likewise.
